TITLE: Sample Hugo Site Configuration (hugo.yml)
DESCRIPTION: This YAML configuration file (`hugo.yml`) provides a comprehensive example for setting up a Hugo site using the PaperMod theme. It includes settings for base URL, title, pagination, theme, robots.txt, build options, minification, and various theme parameters like `env`, `keywords`, `author`, `DateFormat`, `defaultTheme`, and display options. It also covers assets, label, profile mode, home info, social icons, analytics, cover image, post editing, search options, and main menu configuration. Additionally, it specifies settings for Hugo's syntax highlighter (Chroma).

