TITLE: Install Hugo PaperMod Theme using Git Submodule
DESCRIPTION: This command adds the PaperMod repository as a Git submodule to your project. Submodules allow you to include other Git repositories within your own. The `--depth=1` flag creates a shallow submodule. The `git submodule update` command is crucial for initializing and updating submodules, especially after cloning the main repository.

SOURCE: https://github.com/adityatelange/hugo-papermod/blob/master/__wiki__/Installation.md#_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: bash
CODE:
```
git submodule add --depth=1 https://github.com/adityatelange/hugo-PaperMod.git themes/PaperMod
git submodule update --init --recursive
```

