TITLE: Hugo Shortcode for Conditional Markdown Processing
DESCRIPTION: This Hugo shortcode dynamically processes its inner content. It first initializes a scratch variable 'md' to false. It then checks if the shortcode was called with named parameters. If so, it attempts to get the value of the 'md' parameter. Otherwise, it gets the value of the first positional parameter. Finally, it checks the 'md' variable; if it's false, the inner content is rendered as-is. If 'md' is true (or any truthy value), the inner content is passed through the `markdownify` function before rendering.

SOURCE: https://github.com/adityatelange/hugo-papermod/blob/master/layouts/shortcodes/ltr.html#_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: Hugo Template
CODE:
```
{{ $.Scratch.Set "md" false }} {{ if .IsNamedParams }} {{ $.Scratch.Set "md" (.Get "md") }} {{ else }} {{ $.Scratch.Set "md" (.Get 0) }} {{ end }}

{{ if eq ($.Scratch.Get "md") false }} {{ .Inner }} {{ else }} {{ .Inner | markdownify }} {{ end }}
```

