TITLE: Resolve Image Source URL and Attributes in Hugo Template
DESCRIPTION: This Hugo template snippet parses a destination URL, determines if it's absolute or relative, and resolves relative paths to their correct permalinks using page resources. It then constructs a dictionary of HTML attributes for an `<img>` tag, including `alt`, `src`, `title` (HTML escaped), and `loading='lazy'`, merging them with any existing attributes.

