TITLE: Display Author Name in Hugo Template
DESCRIPTION: This Go Template snippet retrieves the author's name, prioritizing the page's 'author' parameter over the site's 'author' parameter. It checks if the author value is an array (string slice or interface slice) and, if so, joins the elements with a comma and space. Otherwise, it displays the author as a single string. This ensures flexible handling of author metadata.

